{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c0e056cb14","title":"打大歼灭战的两个条件","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4fee86b383","index":0,"year":1947,"month":1,"day":25,"articleId":"c0e056cb14"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1e0f28e596","type":"paragraph","text":"打大歼灭战的两个条件！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"c0e056cb14"},{"id":"a23eaf0f90","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年1月25日楚、萧、罗：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"c0e056cb14"},{"id":"3e6d81b8b1","type":"paragraph","text":"打大齐灭战的两个条件：（一）以小部兵力错制敌之其他部分，集中绝对优势兵力打一个故人，决不可同时打两个敌人，也不可将很多兵力使用于钳制方面。（二）以一部打正面，以主力打迁回，决不可以主力打正面，以一部打迁回。希望你们按以上两条检查过去经验，部署新的作战，好好打几个大歼灭战。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"c0e056cb14"},{"id":"d885155160","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"c0e056cb14"},{"id":"355e3af300","type":"paragraph","text":"子有玄[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给晋察冀军区司令员兼政治委员","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"c0e056cb14"}],"page":{"id":"f5465d24df","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"c0e056cb14","start":384,"end":384}}}},"__N_SSG":true}